.\agent\skills\impeccable\reference\document.md:405:- **Frontmatter first, prose second.** Tokens go in the YAML frontmatter; prose contextualizes them. Don't redefine a token value in two places — the frontmatter is normative.
.\agent\skills\impeccable\reference\document.md:409:- **Functional > decorative**: for each token, explain WHERE and WHY it's used, not just WHAT it is.
.\agent\skills\impeccable\reference\document.md:420:- Don't extract every token. Stop at what's actually reused — one-offs pollute the system.
