.\agent\docs\codex-harness-engineering\templates\package-assets\skills\impeccable\reference\extract.md:3:Identify reusable patterns, components, and design tokens, then extract and consolidate them into the design system for systematic reuse.
.\agent\docs\codex-harness-engineering\templates\package-assets\skills\impeccable\reference\extract.md:7:Find the design system, component library, or shared UI directory. Understand its structure: component organization, naming conventions, design token structure, import/export conventions.
